query:
INSERT INTO jobs (userId, videoId, accountId, commentTemplateId, status, scheduledAt, createdAt, updatedAt) 
SELECT 1, v.id, a.id, c.id, 'pending', NOW(), NOW(), NOW()
FROM videos v, accounts a, commentTemplates c
WHERE v.videoUrl LIKE '%v73mkg8%' AND a.platform = 'rumble' AND c.isActive = 1
LIMIT 1
